arStrings.szText: Better. For the first time since... well, a long while.
Whenever you need me, I will be there. And so will Timue.
Yes. I know. Thank you, my friend.
Please, take the amulet. Timue left a message on it for me, but I will not forget the words.
Handing the player a gift: an amulet. This is an item we used earlier in the quest. Timue had written a message on it for Taissa about how healing is a journey--a series of steps.
Perhaps it can help you when you face your own difficult times.
